fullname: Elite Chinese
image_desc: Photo by Elite Chinese on December 15, 2020.
text:
📱Meet our good friend this year! Everybody has seen it, used it, and almost got sick of it! 😷 We all know about QR code, but do you actually understand what it stands for? More importantly, do you know its name in Chinese? 🧐

QR code is an abbreviation of "Quick Response Code.” While this may sound a little abstract, in Chinese, QR code is 二维码(èr wéi mǎ), literally "two-dimensional barcode". Do you find it much easier to understand now?🤩
.
.
.
